title: Production of creamery butter in Canada 2017
summary: The graph shows the Production of creamery in Tonnes Canada during 2017 .
There are several peaks and dips throughout the year .
The maximum value of Production has been recorded for September , and the minimum value has been recorded for August .
gold: Production of creamery decreased sharply in Canada in the period January-June from 11500 to about 8000 . Then it was kind of stable , slightly fluctuating until November , with a rapid growth in December , reaching 10000 by the end of the year .
